---
// src/pages/vision.astro
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
    <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 md:py-20">

        {/* Simple Title */}
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold mb-10 text-center animate-fade-in text-white">
            Our North Star
        </h1>

        {/* Refined plain text content */}
        <div class="max-w-prose mx-auto space-y-6 text-white/85 text-lg leading-relaxed animate-fade-in-delay-1">
            <p>
                It's clear the next few years are pivotal for Artificial Intelligence, particularly here in Europe. We urgently need to cultivate our own strong AI ecosystem and reduce reliance on others. 
            </p>
            <p>
                Our driving ambition is Artificial General Intelligence (AGI). We are focused on contributing to AI that can genuinely think and learn broadly. Achieving this ultimate challenge is the North Star guiding our efforts.
            </p>
            <p>
                This isn't something one person or company can build alone. That’s why we're bringing together a passionate community – students, researchers, builders, everyone interested in this future. Our events, like the hackathons and talks starting in Antwerp, serve as hubs to connect, share knowledge, spark ideas, and motivate each other to dream bigger. We will do all we can to provide the necessary resources for you to realize your potential.
            </p>
            <p>
             We believe we can build an AI hub that attracts the world's best talent not just with exciting challenges, but with a culture and environment people genuinely want to be part of. Let's bring Europe's innovators home.
            </p>
            <p>
                Honestly, building something of this scale is new territory for me [or 'us', depending on perspective]. But I am [we are] completely focused on making it happen. We must sustain this energy, spread the word, and create a movement that becomes impossible to ignore.
            </p>
            <p>
                If this mission resonates with you, if you want to be part of shaping Europe's AI future, then we need you. This endeavour requires everyone who shares the passion.
            </p>
            <p>
                Let's figure this out together. Find us and join the conversation on Discord: <a href="https://discord.gg/m5Hknymurb" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 underline transition-colors">https://discord.gg/m5Hknymurb</a>
            </p>
        </div>

    </main>
</Layout>
